    <div xml:id="PN363-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai<gap quantity="10" reason="lost" unit="character"/>aiyātic ceṟuveṇṭōraiyār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN363">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>iruṅkaṭa luṭuttavip peruṅkaṇ mānila</l>
<l>muṭaiyilai naṭuvaṇat tiṭaipiṟark kiṉṟit</l>
<l>tāmē yāṇṭa vēmaṅ kāvala</l>
<l>riṭutirai maṇaliṉum palarē cuṭupiṇak</l>
<l>kāṭupati yākap pōkit tatta</l>
<l>nāṭu piṟarkoḷac ceṉṟumāyn taṉarē</l>
<l>yataṉāl, nīyuṅ kēṇmati yattai vīyā</l>
<l>tuṭampoṭu niṉṟa vuyiru millai</l>
<l>maṭaṅka luṇmai māyamō vaṉṟē</l>
<l>kaḷḷi vēynta muḷḷiyam puṟaṅkāṭṭu</l>
<l>veḷḷil pōkiya viyalu ḷāṅka</l>
<l>ṇuppilāa vavipuḻukkal</l>
<l>kaikkoṇṭu piṟakkunōkkā</l>
<l>tiḻipiṟappiṉō ṉīyappeṟṟu</l>
<l>nilaṅkala ṉāka vilaṅkupali micaiyu</l>
<l>miṉṉā vaikal vārā muṉṉē</l>
<l>ceynnī muṉṉiya viṉaiyē</l>
<l>munnīr varaippaka muḻutuṭaṉ tuṟantē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">On this big earth of vast area that is encircled by the dark sea, </l>
<l corresp="3">there are protective guardians who rule themselves </l>
<l corresp="2">without [leaving] for others [as much] space as is in the middle of a babul leaf, </l>
<l corresp="4a-c">many more that the [grains of] sand by the sea that puts [them down]. </l>
<l corresp="4d-5c">Having gone, burning corpses, to the cremation ground as [their] abode, </l>
<l corresp="5c-6">as others rule all their lands, they went [and] are gone. </l>
<l corresp="7a-c">Therefore, you too listen [now]: </l>
<l corresp="7d-8">there is no lasting life with the body, unperishing. </l>
<l corresp="9">The existence of Death an illusion? It is not. </l>
<l corresp="10">In the thorny outer cremation ground covered by spurges, </l>
<l corresp="11">in that vast inner place overgrown with woodapple </l>
<l>taking in hand boiled rice as an offering </l>
<l>without salt, not looking behind, (12f.)</l>
<l corresp="14">obtaining when a low-born man gives, </l>
<l corresp="15">on the height of shining offerings with the ground as the vessel, </l>
<l corresp="16">before unpleasant day comes </l>
<l corresp="17">[just] do the work you consider, </l>
<l corresp="18">abandoning altogether the inland bordered by the three-watered sea. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
